name: Deer Creek Ontario fs19
description:
Deer Creek released available; link in the pinned post.

Initially it was a small map done in few weeks for private use. It consists only in: 2 grain farms, one seed and vehicule dealer, anhydrous, seasons, .... ready.

FS22 approaching, it's my last work on FS19. I am sharing it to the community, no ask for modifications.
Thanks to JS modding, Trailer Park Farms, NFEG and others contributors via their mods.
Have a good game and happy halloween
